Conclusion
You have successfully built a comprehensive campaign analysis system using open-source tools. This lab demonstrated how to:

Set up Elasticsearch and Kibana for security data analysis
Create interactive heatmaps to visualize attack patterns
Use ATT&CK Navigator to map techniques to the MITRE framework
Correlate activities across campaigns to identify high-risk areas
